

Loops: -
        Loops are used to repeat a task in a  program.
    
    - There are three types of loops in Java.
    - while loop,
    - for loop,
    - do while loop.

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

    - While loop:
                While loop is run continously till the perticular condition is true, when the condition value got false then the loop stops.

                - Syntax:
                        while(condition){
                            //statement1
                        }

                [$ Special Note : - never make a condition in while loop whose value is always true because it creates a infinite never ending loop.]
    
________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

    - For loop:
                - Syntax:
                        for(initialisation:condition:updation){
                            //statement
                        }


________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

    - Do while loop:
                    - Syntax:
                            do{
                                //statement1
                            } while(condition);

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________


    -- Difference betwwen For loop, While loop and do while loop: -

    For loop: 
            it checks the condition before executing code block, and useful when you know how many time a task is to be repeated.

    While loop:
                it checks the condition before executing the code block but it will continue to execute even if the condition is false.

    Do while loop:
                    it checks the condition after executing the code block, it execute the condition atleast once.

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________

    Break Statement:
                    to exit the loop.


    Continue Keyword:
                    to skip an iteration.

________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________________